Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:44.18,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,WE GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pirates who are \Nafter the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.73,0:02:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...head for the New World, the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.76,0:03:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.32,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.42,0:03:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The New World has ruined many \Npirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.34,0:03:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a boy whose body turned to rubber \Nafter he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.67,0:03:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.33,0:03:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Straw Hats finally \Nentered the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.79,0:03:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the harshest sea ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After receiving an emergency signal, \Nthey landed on Punk Hazard Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a strange island \Ndivided into two parts;
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Burning Lands and the Ice Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sink to your death, Devil Fruit eaters!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:04:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that crap. Let us see \Ninside the laboratory.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.09,0:04:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Straw Hat comes, I'll \Nchop his head off for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's all you have to say, go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two, three...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.61,0:04:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.79,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats?! Children?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got out of the building! I can go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.98,0:04:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering who this \Nvillainous guy was! Smoker!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you, cutie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good! The Navy's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't escape from here! \NLet's look for another exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What brought the Navy to such a place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.70,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know! Just run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, kids! Go to the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, let's catch the Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.63,0:05:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takt!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.71,0:05:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"In a Real Pinch! Luffy Sinks \Ninto the Ice-cold Lake!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:43.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,PUNK HAZARD ISLAND - THE \NMIDDLE LAKE LUFFY'S GROUP
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.55,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim at the bottom of the boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.34,0:06:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.23,0:06:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about, Usopp?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.23,0:06:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no idea what's going on, do you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.61,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to make us fall into the lake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.52,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me - Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.46,0:06:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.49,0:06:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you don't know who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a former pirate with an 80 \Nmillion 60 thousand berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.42,0:06:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brownbeard-sama! Sama... \NSama... Sama... Sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never heard of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.41,0:07:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can they be so ignorant?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this! An angry shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.13,0:07:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, those bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.67,0:07:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes! He did it!\N--That's our Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boat capsized!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.42,0:07:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?! Struggle as much as you like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.76,0:07:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you'll be swallowed by the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body's gonna turn to ice \Nin a matter of minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.02,0:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could've fought back, Duffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.45,0:08:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bud you didn't shtop recruiting zem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.22,0:08:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! My mouth is freebing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zorry. I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.21,0:08:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need zem to join our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.56,0:08:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's finish them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.55,0:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.52,0:08:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.54,0:08:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold these two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna slice them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry up... O-Or I'm gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.58,0:08:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, what happened, Roro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharks!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are sharks in a lake?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's technically a sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.68,0:09:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight between Akainu and Aokiji left \Na crater just like after an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then seawater streamed in from \Na big crack and created a lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.20,0:09:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, so did a lot of sea life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.83,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.60,0:09:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sharks! Scary! Sharks! Zoro \Ngot bitten by a shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim carefully! There is \Nnothing they can do now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no place to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.48,0:09:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blow them to kingdom come!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! I've never thought \Nmy life would end like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.62,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:09:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.58,0:10:04.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is colder than a freezing blizzard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the wind from the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.51,0:10:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did I mention I froze your gun barrels?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they'll explode if you shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, skull mask?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.06,0:10:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is not worth mentioning. It's Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just mentioned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.21,0:10:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a skeleton who came back from \Nthe dead and put my second life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in the hands of the Straw Hat captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.27,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call me Soul King!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did he freeze our guns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.23,0:11:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Unforgivable"? Right back at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.57,0:11:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You bastard!\N--How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.95,0:11:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing friends - I'm sick of it (korigori)!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.46,0:11:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it sounds like ice (koori)!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's fast! He sure can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know they had another crewmember!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.95,0:11:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't matter now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.66,0:11:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because they already became shark food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sharks got their butts kicked!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where did they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.68,0:12:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just in time, Brook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad that you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.08,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chased by a strange thing \Nand happened to come this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try, you part-human-part-animals!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sharks can't stop us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're way stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.23,0:12:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter... how strong we are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't stand the cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing! I'm gonna turn to ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I TOLD YOU GUYS..." I rold you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:46.99,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"WE CAN'T JUST GO TO THE \NCOLD SIDE LIKE THIS...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:46.99,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hust go to the \Ncold shide like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.55,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But look. We're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.23,0:12:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should be glad that we ran into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.21,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss, they're right on top of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! They look familiar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the fourth guy from the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take the guy next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl at the far left.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.31,0:13:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are they talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their clothes look warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:36.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"ALL RIGHT... PLEASE GET ME ONE, TOO!"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.82,0:13:36.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,All right... flease ket me one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they looking to rip our coats off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're terrible! Do they wanna rob us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! That hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.10,0:13:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the rookie of that worst \Ngeneration from two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.92,0:14:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.78,0:14:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is Fire Fist's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.15,0:14:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pirate with a 400 million \Nberry bounty - Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.24,0:14:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4... 400 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mil Fleurs!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.08,0:14:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.21,0:14:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not fight back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't have to hurt you so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.89,0:14:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my friends. You're in \Nbetter shape than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.08,0:15:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:23.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,THE LABORATORY - IN FRONT \NOF THE MAIN ENTRANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.63,0:15:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, Smo-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I said I didn't \Nwant anything to do with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.25,0:15:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.24,0:16:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Hi-ya! It's this way, kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta find a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.82,0:16:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go back! It was that man who cut me up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then he may have the rest of your body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.51,0:16:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it can wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Maybe I can get a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find a backdoor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't go back to face the Navy again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.24,0:16:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any exit! Where is the backdoor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.58,0:16:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Super count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.02,0:16:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got some kind of sensor on you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.06,0:16:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.62,0:16:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why did you take the lead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.16,0:17:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was that samurai...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.68,0:17:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...And the Straw Hats.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Room!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?! It's like a thin film...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shambles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? I felt something weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.83,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No time to think about it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, keep running, brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did I drop my cigarette?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.99,0:18:03.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is no time for you \Nto fool around, Sanji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this week's episode, I'm super!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a backdoor in a moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everybody?\N--There's something wrong with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.53,0:18:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, my \Nbreasts feel lighter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are...! I got big breasts!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.26,0:18:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I turned into a human!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did it happen? I'm a racoon now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.35,0:18:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Everybody, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.80,0:18:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do a roll call!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Chopper!\N--Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.76,0:18:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Franky!\N--Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.68,0:19:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nami... aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.91,0:19:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back our ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.87,0:19:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't have it as it is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's falling toward us!\N--Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.97,0:20:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's retreat for now, Vice \NAdmiral! His power is too creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.32,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.52,0:20:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let anyone leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fused to the rocks of the island?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.86,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made some sort of strange \Nartwork with the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We can't make it back \Nto the base without the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Warlords work for the Government!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.06,0:20:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're breaking your \Ncontract by attacking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.69,0:20:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--We'll report this to headquarters!\N--They'll strip you of your title!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.12,0:21:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.45,0:21:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Transponder Snails?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.72,0:21:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Mine's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way... So is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are ours!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He took all of our Transponder Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you tell the \Nheadquarters or the Government
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.94,0:21:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,about anything that you've \Nseen on this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid pirate, don't push your luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smo-yan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ate the Op-Op Fruit and you're \Nthe Modification Man, I believe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his sword's reach!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.55,0:22:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.22,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But I'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.69,0:22:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are in my way! \NGet out of the circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.26,0:22:13.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.15,0:22:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you're in the circle he created,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.56,0:22:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're like a patient on an operating table!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.84,0:22:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is his operating room.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has total control over it and can \Nmanipulate anything as he pleases!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Surgeon of Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.24,0:22:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trafalgar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.46,0:22:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really wanna do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.39,0:22:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Tashigi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.09,0:22:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Haki is not strong enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.19,0:23:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Tashigi being cut down,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.96,0:23:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the thugs of the Navy's G-5 unit were \Nalso about to face annihilation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then Smoker faces Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.14,0:23:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A duel between a Warlord and a \NNavy Vice-Admiral finally begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their fierce battle that destroys \Neverything around them
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.18,0:23:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,suddenly takes an unexpected turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.81,0:23:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.11,0:23:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Meeting Again After Two Years!\NLuffy and Law!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
